                <mxCell id="parent_calc" value="&lt;b&gt;Parent Node: All 10 instances&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;4 Approve  |  6 Deny&lt;br&gt;H(parent) = −(4/10)·log₂(4/10) − (6/10)·log₂(6/10)&lt;br&gt;= −(0.4)·(−1.322) − (0.6)·(−0.737)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;H(parent) = 0.971 bits&lt;/b&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E8EAF6;strokeColor=#1A237E;fontColor=#1A237E;fontSize=11;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
